summary: I finally got a drawing monitor. I never have time for this but drawing has always been a go to of mine when I’m in a tough...
caption: I finally got a drawing monitor. I never have time for this but drawing has always been a go to of mine when I’m in a tough spot. I just feel so relieved that I can draw, and honestly I can do this all day. I want to get better at drawing digitally. I know I have a long way to go. I just need to practice as much as I can. I found this sketch that I did a while back but was unable to finish it because I had a hard time drawing with a pad. The monitor is so much better. Here is the final product, it’s a mess but I’m proud of it.
